      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "OF"                 to   v-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
       box-cnf-exe-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Box                                             *
